snippet.textDisplay: Beautiful, soulful and mesmerisingly musical song, tastefully written and produced. On our Q Acoustics 3020i the ghungroo shimmering on top with a dry egg-shaker/maraca adding sandy texture; airy “hooo ooooo” background vocals on the left, Ali Sethi locked to a rock-solid phantom center; gentle guitar on the right; tabla tucked behind the vocal plane. Clean imaging, zero smear is like pure silk. The 3020i opened up the mix’s hidden beauty, one could hear the new layers and enjoy this masterpiece even more. Come to our studio if you want experience the same!
snippet.textOriginal: Beautiful, soulful and mesmerisingly musical song, tastefully written and produced.
